N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 192.6 - Quarantine orders

State Regulations

No person shall fail to comply with the provisions of any
quarantine order issued by the department pursuant to ECL section 9-1303. To
the extent any of the provisions of section
192.5
of this Part and any such
quarantine order are in conflict, the more restrictive provision shall
apply. Notes
